HEADWORD: Deipnosophist
<hw>Deip*nos"o*phist</hw> <pr>(d⟦imac⟧p*n⟦ocr⟧s"⟦osl⟧*f⟦icr⟧st)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <grk>deipnosofisth`s</grk>; <grk>dei^pnon</grk>
